These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: coffee, hot-chocolate, 7up, tea
Sport: swimming, surfing, rugby, baseball
1. Beverage:coffee is on the right of Sport:rugby##1
2. Sport:baseball is on the far left##1
3. Sport:rugby is between Sport:surfing and Beverage:hot-chocolate##2
4. Beverage:tea is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:7up is between Beverage:hot-chocolate and Beverage:coffee##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | tea         | hot-chocolate   | 7up | coffee       |
| Sport      | baseball | swimming | rugby   | surfing |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: woodworking, writing, rock-climbing, photography
Nationality: thai, polish, indian, italian
1. Nationality:italian is between Hobby:rock-climbing and Nationality:polish##2
2. Hobby:photography is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:indian is on the right of Nationality:thai##1
4. Hobby:woodworking is on the left of Nationality:thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | writing | woodworking | rock-climbing | photography |
| Nationality   | polish    | italian   | thai | indian       |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
