Nationality: malaysian, indian, italian, russian
1. Nationality:italian is on the right of Food:avocado##1
2. Nationality:italian is between Nationality:indian and Food:garlic##2
3. Nationality:indian is on the far left##1
4. Nationality:russian is on the left of Food:strawberry##1
5. Food:garlic == Nationality:russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | avocado    | orange | garlic   | strawberry  |
| Nationality   | indian | italian   | russian | malaysian |

